From 7a8c76b5e8eb06e6127db075cf1f6b67c436fd96 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marco Collovati <marco@vaadin.com>
Date: Tue, 23 May 2023 10:51:34 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] fix: remove detach listener when javascript execution
 completes (#16836) (#16853)

A detach listener is added for pending javascript invocation owner nodes
to clean up the queue, if the owner gets detached.
This change also removes the detach listener when the javascript execution
completes.
